title: 'The Rehearsal', Season 1
description:
The Ringer's Bill Simmons is joined by Juliet Litman to discuss Nathan Fielder’s return to TV in HBO’s bizarre show ‘The Rehearsal’.

Hosts: Bill Simmons and Juliet Litman
Producer: Kyle Crichton
